<br>
If you're one of the few people who did the quest twice and lost an earring due to it being made lore, petition in game and a GM will reimburse you with the nine ingredients needed to make another earring after verifying your loss.<br>
<br>
If your Xanthe's Earring is out of charges, trade it in with Rebecca Cabbageleaf in Fungusgrove, and she'll give you one that has charges.  When items that didn't have an effect are retroactively changed, it sometimes causes the &quot;out of charges&quot; bug.  <br>
<br>
To trade the earring in with Rebecca, give her your Xanthe's Earring and she'll give you an alternate kind of earring.  Give her back the alternate earring, and she'll give you a fully charged Xanthe's earring back.<br>
<br>
Sorry for any inconvenience this has caused you, this should solve any difficulties anyone's had with the earring.<br>
<br>
Thanks,<br>
<br>
